	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />WedNESday can do both vertical and horizontal scrolling including split screen scrolling no problem. Also, WedNESday ignores the PPU documents (341 ppu cc etc.) and just renders the scanline normally (i.e. it just fetches 1 tile every 8 pixels and renders it). I know that some of you may think that this would make the emulator run incorrectly but most (90%) NROM games (no mapper support yet) run perfectly (still some PPU work to do).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
