		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />He means you'll have issues with games which do mid-scanline effects like Final Fantasy, Marble Madness, Micro Machines, and several others.
<br />
<br />Rounding off when Sprite-0 hit happens could affect games as well... if you're rounding off to the start or end of the scanline which sprite 0 hit happens, several games will have display problems.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
